Speaker.P:
My Department is responsible for the issue of licences under section 23 of the Wildlife Acts 1976 and 2000 to the Department of Agriculture and Food to capture and humanely kill badgers as part of its continued research into bovine tuberculosis. The numbers of licences issued since 1995 are as follows:  
1995, 
337 licences; 
1996, 
329 licences; 
1997, 
423 licences; 
1998, 
361 licences; 
1999, 
503 licences; 
2000, 
591 licences; 
2001,
477 licences; 
2002, 
810 licences; 
2003, 
383licences.
